name: R4B-ManufacturedItemDefinition-R5-ManufacturedItemDefinition
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R4B ManufacturedItemDefinition into FHIR R5

element.display: The definition and characteristics of a medicinal manufactured item, such as a tablet or capsule, as contained in a packaged medicinal product

target.display: The definition and characteristics of a medicinal manufactured item, such as a tablet or capsule, as contained in a packaged medicinal product
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition`
R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.contained` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.contained`

R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.extension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R4B `extension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `extension`
R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.id` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.id`
R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.identifier` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.identifier`

element.display: A set of rules under which this content was created

target.display: A set of rules under which this content was created
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.implicitRules` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.implicitRules`

element.display: The ingredients of this manufactured item. Only needed if these are not specified by incoming references from the Ingredient resource

target.display: The ingredients of this manufactured item. Only needed if these are not specified by incoming references from the Ingredient resource
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.ingredient` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.ingredient`

R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.language` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.language` - language made the binding required (from Preferred) for http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/all-languages|5.0.0

element.display: Dose form as manufactured (before any necessary transformation)

target.display: Dose form as manufactured (before any necessary transformation)
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.manufacturedDoseForm` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.manufacturedDoseForm`

element.display: Manufacturer of the item (Note that this should be named "manufacturer" but it currently causes technical issues)

target.display: Manufacturer of the item, one of several possible
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.manufacturer` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.manufacturer`
R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.meta` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.meta`

R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.modifierExtension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R4B `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `modifierExtension`
R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property`

R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.extension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R4B `extension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `extension`
R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.id` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.id`

element.display: Extensions that cannot be ignored even if unrecognized

target.display: Extensions that cannot be ignored even if unrecognized
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.modifierExtension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R4B `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `modifierExtension`

element.display: A code expressing the type of characteristic

target.display: A code expressing the type of characteristic
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.type` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.type`

R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.value[x]` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.value[x]` - value[x] has change due to type change: R4B `value[x]` `Attachment` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `value[x]`

R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.status` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.status` - status has compatible required binding for code type: http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/publication-status|4.3.0 and http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/publication-status|5.0.0 (Equivalent)

element.display: Text summary of the resource, for human interpretation

target.display: Text summary of the resource, for human interpretation
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.text` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.text`

element.display: The “real world” units in which the quantity of the item is described

target.display: The “real-world” units in which the quantity of the item is described
target.comment: R4B `ManufacturedItemDefinition.unitOfPresentation` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition.unitOfPresentation`
